Package se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.api.analyzer.patterns

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MavenModelPatterns
    Holder specification for Patterns intended to validate or invalidate data retrieved from a Maven POM.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMavenModelPatterns
    Abstract/generic holder implementation of the MavenModelPatterns specification.
    DefaultProjectParentPatterns
    Default MavenModelPatterns implementation for a project parent POM, typically on the following form: <parent> <groupId>se.jguru.nazgul.core.poms.core-parent</groupId> <artifactId>nazgul-core-parent</artifactId> </parent> <groupId>com.acme.foobar.poms.foobar-parent</groupId> <artifactId>foobar-parent</artifactId>
    DefaultTopReactorPatterns
    Default MavenModelPatterns implementation for a top-level reactor POM, typically on the following form: <parent> <groupId>se.jguru.nazgul.tools.poms.external</groupId> <artifactId>nazgul-tools-external-reactor-parent</artifactId> </parent> <groupId>com.acme.foobar</groupId> <artifactId>foobar-reactor</artifactId>
